# Galperyn Renovation Website

This is the official website for **Galperyn Renovation**, a company specializing in home remodeling and renovation services. The website showcases our services, portfolio, and provides a way for potential clients to get in touch.

## Description
Galperyn Renovation offers high-quality renovation services including:
- Kitchen Renovations
- Bathroom Remodeling
- Full-Home Renovations
- Custom Design & Builds
- Additions and Extensions

The website provides an overview of our work, services, and contact information, aiming to help clients transform their homes into dream spaces.

## How to Use
Visit the website at:
[https://yourusername.github.io/galperyn-renovation](https://yourusername.github.io/galperyn-renovation)

To explore our portfolio, check out the services we offer, or request a free quote, click on the corresponding sections on the homepage.

## How to Contribute
1. Fork this repository.
2. Create a branch for your changes (`git checkout -b feature-branch`).
3. Commit your changes (`git commit -am 'Add new feature'`).
4. Push to your branch (`git push origin feature-branch`).
5. Submit a pull request to the main repository.

